snippet.title: Splash Blast Panic | Alpha Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Splash Blast Panic | Second Alpha Trailer 

Splash Blast Panic is a party multiplayer game where you must fight your opponent using waterguns, stomps, superattacks and of course, your wits ! Play up to 4 players with a lot of options to setup games to your liking, wide set of stages and characters and unleash watery hell upon your opponent.

---

This game is still in alpha, hence most of what you see will change before the final release.

Team KwaKwa members:
Elias Farhan - Programmer, Game Designer
Kevin Péclet - Artist, Co-designer
Mitch Gasser - Composer
